      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JEANNA (2) has found the minor placings here at last couple of runs, finishing second last time beaten one length (22.50). Good beginner aided by a nice draw. One of the contenders. SAVINA (7) missed the frame latest but had been racing well prior to that including a Maiden win two back (23.16) at The Gardens. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. BARGAIN BETTY (8) was prominent throughout when winning two back then got further back last time but came home hard into third and beaten 2 lengths at Taree Super Track (17.77). Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Winning chance. STUMPY JONES (1) is worth consideration.",
